Steps for your initial set up for Spring, Hibernate, Database and the packages you need for your project

1.Create a dynamic project
2. Add to lib -> MySQl conector 
3. Test the connection 
	3.1 create a servlet
4. Copy and update spring-config and web-inf xml files on WEB-INF folder

5.Add to lib javax.servlet.jsp.jstl-1.2.1 and javax.servlet.jsp.jstl-api-1.2.1
6. Download spring release riles www.luv2.com/downloadspring and copy all lib files
7. Download hibernate files hibernate.org/orm/downloads
	only required files AND optional C3PO and paste them

8. Test MVC Controller
	8.1 create the controller
	8.2 Create the page (WEB-INF create view folder)

9. Hands on :)
 	9.1 Controller, service, dao, entity